\c 29
\s Ukugcotshwa kukaAroni lamadodana akhe
\p
\v 1 Yile-ke into ozayenza kubo ukubehlukanisa ukuthi bangisebenzele njengabapristi. Thatha ijongosi elilodwa ithole lenkomo\x + Levi 8.2; 9.2.\x*, lenqama ezimbili ezingelasici,
\v 2 lesinkwa esingelamvubelo\x + Levi 2.4; 6.20-22.\x*, lamaqebelengwana angelamvubelo ahlanganiswe lamafutha, lezinkwana eziyizipatalala ezingelamvubelo ezinindwe ngamafutha, uzenze ngempuphu ecolekileyo yengqoloyi;
\v 3 ukufake esitsheni esisodwa, ukusondeze ngesitsha, kanye lejongosi lenqama ezimbili.
\v 4 Usondeze uAroni lamadodana akhe emnyango wethente lenhlangano, ubagezise ngamanzi\x + 40.12; Levi 8.6; Heb. 10.22.\x*;
\v 5 uthathe izembatho\x + 28.2,4.\x*, ugqokise uAroni isigqoko, lebhatshi \w le-efodi\w**, le-efodi, lesembatho sesifuba, umbophe ngebhanti elelukwe ngobungcitshi le-efodi\x + 28.8.\x*,
\v 6 u\add m\add*thwalise iqhiye ekhanda lakhe\x + 28.36,37; Levi 8.9; 21.12; Nani 6.7.\x*, u\add m\add*thwalise umqhele ongcwele phezu kweqhiye.
\v 7 Uthathe amafutha okugcoba\x + 28.21; 28.41. 30.25,30. Levi 8.12,30. 10.7. 21.10. Nani 35.25.\x*, uwathele ekhanda lakhe, umgcobe.
\v 8 Usondeze lamadodana akhe\x + Levi 8.13.\x*, uwagqokise izigqoko.
\v 9 Ubabophe ngamabhanti\x + 29.15,19. Levi 1.4.\x*, uAroni lamadodana akhe, ubabophele izingowane, lobupristi bube ngobabo ngesimiso saphakade\x + 27.21. Nani 18.7.\x*. Ubehlukanise-ke uAroni lamadodana akhe.
\v 10 Uzasondeza ijongosi phambi kwethente lenhlangano; njalo uAroni lamadodana akhe babeke izandla zabo enhlokweni yejongosi\x + 29.15,19. Levi 1.4.\x*;
\v 11 ubusulihlaba ijongosi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* emnyango wethente lenhlangano,
\v 12 uthathe okwegazi lejongosi\x + Levi 8.15.\x*, ulifake empondweni zelathi\x + 27.2; 30.2.\x* ngomunwe wakho, uthululele lonke igazi esisekelweni selathi.
\v 13 Uzathatha idanga lonke\x + 29.22. Levi 3.3.\x*, lamahwahwa aphezu kwesibindi, lezinso zombili, lamahwahwa aphezu kwazo, ukutshise elathini.
\v 14 Kodwa inyama yejongosi lesikhumba salo lomswane walo ukutshise ngomlilo ngaphandle kwenkamba\x + Levi 4.11,12,21. Nani 19.3,5. Heb. 13.11.\x*; kungumnikelo wesono.
\p
\v 15 Ubusuthatha inqama ibenye\x + 29.1. Levi 8.18.\x*; njalo uAroni lamadodana akhe babeke izandla zabo phezu kwenhloko yenqama\x + 29.10,19.\x*.
\v 16 Ubusuyihlaba inqama, uthathe igazi layo, ulifafaze elathini uligombolozele.
\v 17 Uyiqume inqama ngeziqa zayo, ugezise imibilini yayo lemilenze yayo, ukubeke phezu kweziqa zayo laphezu kwenhloko yayo,
\v 18 utshise inqama yonke elathini. Kungumnikelo wokutshiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, kuluqhatshi olumnandi, umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo\x + Gen. 8.21; Eks. 29.25,41.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Uzathatha inqama yesibili\x + 29.1. Levi 8.22.\x*; uAroni lamadodana akhe babesebebeka izandla zabo phezu kwenhloko yenqama\x + 29.10,15.\x*.
\v 20 Uyihlabe-ke inqama, uthathe okwegazi layo, ulifake eqwangeni lwendlebe kaAroni, leqwangeni lwendlebe yokunene yamadodana akhe, lesithupheni sesandla sabo sokunene, lezwaneni olukhulu lonyawo lwabo lokunene, ufafaze igazi elathini uligombolozele.
\v 21 Uthathe okwegazi eliselathini lokwamafutha okugcoba\x + 29.7.\x*, ukufafaze phezu kukaAroni, laphezu kwezembatho zakhe, laphezu kwamadodana akhe, laphezu kwezembatho zamadodana akhe kanye laye, ukuze abe ngcwele lezembatho zakhe, lamadodana akhe lezembatho zamadodana akhe kanye laye.
\v 22 Uthathe enqameni amahwahwa, lomsila ononileyo, ledanga\x + 29.13.\x*, lamahwahwa esibindi\x + 29.13.\x*, lezinso zombili, lamahwahwa aphezu kwazo, lomlenze wokunene, ngoba iyinqama yokwehlukaniswa\x + 29.26,27,31,34. Levi 7.37. 8.28,31,33.\x*;
\v 23 lesinkwa esiyindilinga esisodwa\x + 29.2,3. Levi 8.26.\x*, leqebelengwana elilodwa elesinkwa esilamafutha, lesinkwana esiyisipatalala esisodwa, esitsheni sezinkwa ezingelamvubelo esiphambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*,
\v 24 ukubeke konke ezandleni zikaAroni lezandleni zamadodana akhe\x + 28.41.\x*, ukuzunguze ukuze kube ngumnikelo wokuzunguzwa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 25 Ukuthathe ezandleni zabo\x + 29.18,41. Levi 6.22. 8.28.\x*, ukutshise phezu kwelathi phezu komnikelo wokutshiswa, ukuze kube luqhatshi olumnandi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*; kungumnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo.
\v 26 Uzathatha isifuba senqama yokwehlukaniswa engekaAroni, usizunguze sibe ngumnikelo wokuzunguzwa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, njalo sibe yisabelo sakho.
\v 27 Uzasingcwelisa isifuba somnikelo wokuzunguzwa\x + Levi 7.31,34. 8.29.10.14,15. Nani 18.11,18.\x* lomlenze womnikelo wokuphakanyiswa ozunguzwayo lophakanyiswayo\x + 29.28.25.2,3. Levi 7.32,34. 10.15. Nani 18.11.\x*, okwenqama yokwehlukaniswa, okwalokho okungokukaAroni lokwalokho okungokwamadodana akhe;
\v 28 njalo kuzakuba ngokukaAroni lokwamadodana akhe, kube yisimiso saphakade kuvela kubantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 27.21.\x*; ngoba kungumnikelo wokuphakanyiswa; kuzakuba ngumnikelo wokuphakanyiswa ovela kubantwana bakoIsrayeli, eminikelweni yabo yokuthula; umnikelo wabo wokuphakanyiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\p
\v 29 Lezembatho ezingcwele zikaAroni zizakuba ngezamadodana akhe emva kwakhe, ukuze agcotshwe embethe zona\x + Nani 18.8.\x*, lokuze ehlukaniswe embethe zona\x + 29.9.\x*.
\v 30 Insuku eziyisikhombisa\x + Levi 8.35.\x* umpristi endaweni yakhe, ovela kumadodana akhe\x + Nani 20.28.\x*, uzazembatha, nxa engena ethenteni lenhlangano ukukhonza e\add ndaw\add*eni engcwele.
\p
\v 31 Uzathatha-ke inqama yokwehlukaniswa, upheke inyama yayo endaweni engcwele\x + Levi 8.31.\x*.
\v 32 Njalo uAroni lamadodana akhe bazakudla inyama yenqama lesinkwa esisesitsheni\x + Levi 8.31.\x* emnyango wethente lenhlangano,
\v 33 badle lezozinto okwenziwa ngazo inhlawulo yokuthula\x + Mat. 12.4.\x*, ukubehlukanisa, ukubangcwelisa; kodwa owemzini angazidli ngoba zingcwele\x + Levi 22.10.\x*.
\v 34 Njalo uba kusala okwenyama yokwehlukaniswa kumbe okwesinkwa kuze kuse, tshisa okuseleyo ngomlilo\x + Levi 8.32.\x*; kungadliwa, ngoba kungcwele.
\p
\v 35 Uzakwenza njalo-ke kuAroni lakumadodana akhe njengakho konke engikulaya khona; insuku eziyisikhombisa uzabehlukanisa\x + Levi 8.33-35.\x*.
\v 36 Insuku ngensuku unikele ijongosi lomnikelo wesono\x + 29.14; 30.10.\x* wenhlawulo yokuthula; uhlambulule ilathi lapho ulenzela inhlawulo yokuthula, uligcobe ukuze ulingcwelise\x + 30.26,28,29; 40.10.\x*.
\v 37 Ulenzele ilathi inhlawulo yokuthula insuku eziyisikhombisa, ulingcwelise, lelathi lizakuba yingcwelengcwele\x + 40.10.\x*; konke okulithintayo ilathi kuzakuba ngcwele\x + 30.29. Mat. 23.19.\x*.
\s Iminikelo yensuku ngensuku
\p
\v 38 Yilokhu-ke ozakunikela phezu kwelathi: Amawundlu amabili alomnyaka owodwa\x + Nani 28.3. 1 Lan. 16.40. 2 Lan. 2.4.13.11. 31.3. Ezra 3.3.\x* insuku ngensuku njalonjalo\x + Dan. 8.11-13. 9.27. 12.11. Heb. 10.11.\x*.
\v 39 Elinye iwundlu uzalinikela ekuseni\x + 2 Kho. 16.15. Hez. 46.13,14,15.\x*, lelinye iwundlu ulinikele kusihlwa,
\v 40 lokwetshumi kwempuphu ecolekileyo kuxubene lengxenye yesine \w yehini\w** yamafutha agigiweyo, lengxenye yesine \w yehini\w** yewayini kube ngumnikelo wokunathwayo, welinye iwundlu.
\v 41 Lelinye iwundlu ulinikele kusihlwa\x + 1 Kho. 18.29,36. 2 Kho. 16.15. Ezra 9.4,5. Hlab. 141.2. Dan. 9.21.\x*, wenze kulo njengomnikelo wokudla wekuseni\x + 1 Kho. 18.29,36. 2 Kho. 16.15. Ezra 9.4,5. Hlab. 141.2. Dan. 9.21.\x*, lanjengomnikelo wawo wokunathwayo, kube luqhatshi olumnandi\x + 29.18,25.\x*, umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo.
\v 42 \add Uzakuba\add* ngumnikelo wokutshiswa njalonjalo ezizukulwaneni zenu\x + Nani 28.6. Eks. 30.8.\x*, emnyango wethente lenhlangano phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, lapho engizahlangana khona lani\x + 25.22. 30.6,36. Nani 17.4.\x*, ukukhuluma lawe lapho.
\v 43 Lalapho ngizahlangana labantwana bakoIsrayeli, njalo kungcweliswe yinkazimulo yami\x + 40.34. 1 Kho. 8.11. 2 Lan. 5.14. 7.1,2,3. Hez. 43.5. Hag. 2.7,9. Mal. 3.1.\x*.
\v 44 Njalo ngizangcwelisa ithente lenhlangano lelathi\x + Levi 21.15. 22.9,16.\x*, ngizangcwelisa loAroni lamadodana akhe, ukuze bangisebenzele njengabapristi.
\v 45 Ngizahlala phakathi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Eks. 25.8. Zek. 2.10. Levi 26.12. 2 Kor. 6.16. Isam. 21.3.\x*, ngibe nguNkulunkulu kubo.
\v 46 Bazakwazi-ke ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wabo\x + 20.2.\x*, eyabakhupha elizweni leGibhithe ukuze ngihlale phakathi kwabo; ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wabo.